Swedish tyres, process equipment andcomponents firm &lt;Trelleborg AB> said it was taking a largerstake in mining and metals concern Boliden AB &lt;BLDS.ST> than ithad originally intended.    Trelleborg had previously announced it was exercising anoption to acquire up to 65 pct of Boliden's voting rights.    In a statement, the company said they had received offersof up to 68 pct of the rights, and that they would accept all. Reuter&#3;